.DS_Store
/.build
/.swiftpm
# Library: consumers resolve their own versions, so the lockfile isn't tracked.
/Package.resolved
/Packages
xcuserdata/
*.xcodeproj

# Harness: a standalone Xcode example app, NOT part of the Swift package. Its
# project is generated by Harness/generate_project.rb — commit the generator and
# sources, not the generated project (already covered by *.xcodeproj above) or its
# build output. SwiftMail lives only inside the generated project, never in the
# committed tree, so it never touches the package's dependency graph.
/Harness/build/
/Harness/DerivedData/
